provisions.content:
(a)        “foodstuff” means any of the following classes of commodities:__
(i)        wheat, wheat atta, maida, rawa and suji;
(ii)       rice and paddy;
(iii)      sugar; and
(iv)       such other commodity or class of commodities as may be declared and
notified by the Government to be foodstuffs for the purposes of this Act;
(b)        “Government” means the Government o West Pakistan ; and
(c)        “notified order” means an order notified in the Official Gazette.
